lyrics:
[verse]
Dr. Herbstman's got a dream, you see
To trade in drills for a recipe
In his white coat, he's got a plan
He wants to bake cakes, with spatula in hand

[chorus]
Oh, Dr. Herbstman's got that baking vibe
Mixing flour, sugar, with a little stride
He's got a sweet tooth and a dream to chase
In the kitchen, this dentist wants his place
